    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fanatic of a fictional Christian heresy has a bloody past. Can he find redemption? Become a <br>better person? That's up to you: don't kill anybody or kill everybody and see the story unfold. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive dialog: some options will lead to physical confrontations while others to a pacific resolution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spare the life of your opponents or kill them: the choice is yours(It can affect the story).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic party: depending on your choices you might end up with different companions, or even alone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn based combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 different endings: bad ending, pagan ending, christian ending and evil ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand drawn 2d graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Native 2K and 4k sprites and backgrounds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21:9 support.</p></li></ul>",
